premise_source_doc_sentence: Harry Styles : Live on Tour is the debut concert tour by British recording artist Harry Styles in support of his debut album , Harry Styles  (  2017  )  .

His most recent work includes producer and co-writer of Harry Styles solo debut album Harry Styles  (  album  )  as well as producer and co-writer of Young the Giant 's third album Home of the Strange .
Harry Styles is the debut studio album by English singer and songwriter Harry Styles .
`` Sign of the Times '' is the debut solo single by English singer and songwriter Harry Styles for his self-titled debut studio album .
